# Playwright Automation Framework

UI test automation framework built with Playwright using the Page Object Model (POM) design pattern.

## Project Overview

This project automates end-to-end test scenarios for the SauceDemo web application.
It includes validations for:

- Login functionality
- Inventory page
- Cart page
- Checkout flow
- Negative scenarios and error validations

The framework is designed to be clean, scalable, and easy to maintain.

---

## Tech Stack

- Playwright
- JavaScript
- Node.js
- Page Object Model (POM)

---

## Project Structure

```bash
playwright-project/
├── pages/
│   ├── LoginPage.js
│   ├── InventoryPage.js
│   ├── CartPage.js
│   └── CheckoutPage.js
├── tests/
│   ├── login.spec.js
│   ├── inventory.spec.js
│   └── checkout.spec.js
├── utils/
│   └── testData.js
├── playwright.config.js
├── package.json
└── README.md